    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mystery Company</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Crescentland is under siege. Across farms, harbors, and forgotten towns, supernatural creatures are terrorizing innocent people.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  The Harvest Phantom stalks empty fields. Ghost pirates haunt foggy ports. A massive Leviathan lurks beneath coastal waters.        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  But nothing is as it seems.                                                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > You are Ace, a former detective with a food stand, an old van, and a stubborn refusal to believe in monsters. When an anonymous tip points to NEXUS Industries, a shadowy corporation buying up terrified communities at rock-bottom prices, you begin an investigation that will span an entire nation.                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Every phantom has a face. Every monster has a motive. And someone called &quot;The Architect&quot; is pulling all the strings.               </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Investigate Mysteries</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Travel across 24 distinct zones, from quiet farming villages to industrial port cities. Each location harbors its own mystery waiting to be solved. Gather clues, collect evidence, and unmask the villain behind every haunting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras/7ecbe96f630b442f99a78b86ec0fe0ce.avif?t=1768923864\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras_big/7ecbe96f630b442f99a78b86ec0fe0ce.webp?t=1768923864 width=1560 height=884 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Mysteries scale in difficulty as you solve them. Return to completed zones for greater challenges and better rewards. The deeper you dig, the more you uncover about the conspiracy threatening Crescentland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build Your Agency</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  What begins as a one-person operation grows into a full detective agency. Recruit former allies who share your mission:            </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jo Blackwood</strong> - Your old partner, a tech specialist whose systems were hacked by NEXUS                                   </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Max Torres</strong> - A mechanic whose garage stands in the way of corporate expansion                                           </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Luna</strong> - A specialist with her own reasons to see NEXUS exposed                                                           </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Assign your team to automate operations while you focus on investigations. Each member levels up, unlocking cost reductions and the ability to handle multiple tasks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Everything</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>The Garage</strong>                                                                                                                  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Your van is your lifeline. Upgrade its engine, fuel capacity, storage, and special components. Unlock maintenance systems, turbo boosters, and warp drives for instant travel. Collect gears passively or through exploration. Reach higher van tiers to access distant zones.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>ClueWorks Laboratory</strong>                                                                                                        </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Research new technologies to enhance every aspect of your operation. Unlock automation features, boost resource generation, improve excavation robots, and gain powerful quality-of-life upgrades. Over 50 research projects await completion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras/d9e1e801ab9ade3bf61f3c04b0cd4841.avif?t=1768923864\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras_big/d9e1e801ab9ade3bf61f3c04b0cd4841.webp?t=1768923864 width=1560 height=884 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <strong>The Shelter</strong>                                                                                                                 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Construct and upgrade your headquarters. Place specialized rooms on an expandable grid, creating synergies between adjacent facilities. Defensive structures protect against villain counter-attacks. Every room serves a purpose in your growing empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras/ce5511ae7aecb1446ba2cc385c6986ca.avif?t=1768923864\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras_big/ce5511ae7aecb1446ba2cc385c6986ca.webp?t=1768923864 width=1560 height=884 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Run a Fast Food Empire</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Investigations cost money. Your solution: a fast food franchise network.                                                           </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Purchase locations across Crescentland. Upgrade them through ten tiers, from roadside stands to flagship restaurants. Manage customer satisfaction by balancing menu complexity with demand. Produce snacks used to fuel team operations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Your franchises generate income while you sleep. Expand your network to increase production, unlock new recipes, and dominate the food industry of every zone you liberate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Excavate the Underground</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Beneath the surface lies a network of biomes rich with resources. Navigate grid-based excavation zones, digging through tiles to uncover coins, crystals, rare items, and treasure chests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras/48c153605097da0933f7dc9549fb7d46.avif?t=1768923864\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4318020/extras_big/48c153605097da0933f7dc9549fb7d46.webp?t=1768923864 width=1560 height=884 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Nine distinct underground environments await, each with unique themes, challenges, and rewards. Deploy an excavation robot to continue mining while away. Upgrade its fuel efficiency, durability, and pathfinding capabilities. Build combo chains for bonus tile reveals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Idle Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Mystery Company respects your time. Systems continue operating whether you are actively playing or away:                           </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Franchises accumulate coins and snacks                                                                                         </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The garage collects gears passively                                                                                            </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Underground robots excavate automatically                                                                                      </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Energy and fuel regenerate over time                                                                                           </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Team members execute scheduled tasks                                                                                           </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Offline rewards await your return                                                                                              </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Research idle operations technology to maximize gains while away. Extended absence generates resources based on your progress, player level, and current zone.                                                                                                    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Uncover the Conspiracy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  NEXUS Industries is not just buying property. They are building something. Underground tunnel networks connect their acquisitions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Shell companies obscure their true reach. Military-grade technology surfaces in unlikely places.                                   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Every zone solved reveals another piece of the puzzle. Every villain unmasked provides evidence against the corporation. The truth about The Architect and their ultimate plan unfolds across hundreds of mysteries spanning Crescentland.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 24 unique zones across farming towns, coastal resorts, industrial cities, and more                                             </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Hundreds of mysteries with scaling difficulty and rewards                                                                      </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Deep upgrade systems across garage, shelter, and research                                                                      </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Fast food empire management with satisfaction mechanics                                                                        </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Grid-based underground excavation with nine biomes                                                                             </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Team recruitment and automation with character progression                                                                     </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Villain encounters with capture mechanics                                                                                      </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Offline progression and idle reward systems                                                                                    </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Original story following the NEXUS Industries conspiracy                                                                       </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cross-platform cloud saves                                                                                                     </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Mystery Awaits</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Crescentland needs a detective willing to look behind the masks. Someone who sees through the phantom schemes to the corporate greed beneath. Someone who will not stop until the truth is exposed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  The van is gassed up. The investigation board is ready. Mystery Company is open for business.                                      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                                                                                                                     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <i>Every monster has a motive. Find it.</i> </p>",
